    <body>
        <div xml:id="AN11-kilavi"></div>
        <div xml:id="AN11">
            <lg type="edition"><l>vāṉa mūrnta <choice><seg>vayaṅkoḷi</seg><seg>vayaṅkoḷir</seg></choice> maṇṭila</l>
<l>neruppeṉac civanta vuruppavi raṅkāṭ</l>
<l>ṭilaiyiṉ malarnta <choice><seg>mutaiyi</seg><seg>mukaiyi</seg></choice> lilavaṅ</l>
<l>kaliko ḷāya maliputoku <choice><seg>pētatta</seg><seg>peṭutta</seg></choice></l>
<l>vañcuṭar neṭuṅkoṭi poṟpat <choice><seg>tōṉṟik</seg><seg>tōṉṟuṅ</seg></choice></l>
<l>kayantuka ḷākiya payantapu kāṉa</l>
<l>memmoṭu kaḻintaṉa rāyiṟ kammeṉa</l>
<l><choice><seg>vampuvirit</seg><seg>vampuvirin</seg></choice> taṉṉa poṅkumaṇaṟ <choice><seg>kāṉiyāṟṟup</seg><seg>kāṉyāṟṟup</seg></choice></l>
<l>paṭuciṉai tāḻnta payiliṇa rekkar</l>
<l>meypuku vaṉṉa kaikavar muyakka</l>
<l>mavarum peṟukuvar maṉṉē nayavara</l>
<l>nīrvār <choice><seg>nitamalar</seg><seg>nikarmalar</seg></choice> kaṭuppa vōmaṟan</l>
<l>taṟukuḷa niṟaikku<supplied>na</supplied> pōla vaikalu</l>
<l>maḻutaṉ mēvala vākip</l>
<l>paḻitīr kaṇṇum paṭukuva maṉṉē.</l></lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>In the pretty wilderness shining with heat, when the glowing</l>
<l><choice><seg>	shining bright </seg><seg>	resplendent </seg></choice> orb that climbs the sky has become red like fire,</l>
<l><choice><seg>	when </seg><seg>	where </seg></choice> the <choice><seg>wild </seg><seg>budless </seg></choice> red silk-cotton trees that bloomed without leaves</l>
<l rend="indent">	appear like pretty glowing long banners,</l>
<l rend="indent">	collectively <choice><seg>being the cause of </seg><seg>raised in </seg></choice> joy <choice><seg>for </seg><seg>by </seg></choice> clamouring groups of girls,</l>
<l>through the barren forest where ponds have become dust,</l>
<l>if he <choice><seg>had </seg><seg>has </seg></choice> passed with us, silently<note place="foot">Here the old commentary glosses the ideophone kammeṉa with viraiya, “hastily”, which does not seem to fit the context: SHE wishing that HE had taken her along for his quest after wealth, a post-marital undertaking.</note>,</l>
<l rend="indent">	by the forest river with whirling sands as if newly <choice><seg>expanded,</seg><seg>expanding,</seg></choice> </l>
<l><choice><seg>	through </seg><seg>	in </seg></choice> the dunes with dense clusters that hang down from moving branches</l>
<l>he too would surely have obtained</l>
<l>an embrace that seizes [his] hands as if entering the body.</l>
<l rend="indent">	Longingly,</l>
<l>do they resemble <choice><seg>daily </seg><seg>lustrous </seg></choice> blossoms, overflowing with water?</l>
<l>Having become such as wish to cry</l>
<l>daily, so as to resemble arid ponds filling up, forgetting,</l>
<l>[my] eyes too would surely close without guilt.</l></lg>
        </div>
    </body>
